        },
        {
            "title": "川普就納稅申報表洩露事件起訴美國國稅局和財政部 索賠100億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普就其首個任期內其納稅申報表遭到未經授權披露一事起訴美國國稅局和財政部，要求索賠至少100億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該訴訟已提交至邁阿密聯邦法院。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Sues IRS, Treasury for $10 Billion Over Tax-Return Leaks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%B1%E7%B4%8D%E7%A8%85%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E6%B4%A9%E9%9C%B2%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%85%E5%B1%80%E5%92%8C%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8-%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0100%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-002943447.html",
